snippet.title: Best VGM 1106 - Bit.Trip Flux - Strange Comfort
snippet.description:
Buy the album @ http://www.cdbaby.com/cd/gaijingames6

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo Wii / 3DS
Bit.Trip Flux (2011)
Strange Comfort
Bit Shifter
